<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4747212>
    dc:description "Figure 29. Smittipora abyssicola (Smitt); NHMUK 1999.8.9.4; Recent, west of East Channel, Aldabra Island, 22/11/1967; (a) dried colony; (b) avicularia and autozooids, one ovicellate (arrowed); (c) two autozooids, the one on the left with operculum and part of the frontal cuticle intact; (d) autozooids with cuticles partially preserved and two avicularia with open mandibles. Scale bars: a = 1 mm; b = 200 µm; c = 100 µm; d = 500 µm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4747212/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

